    "description": "<strong>Avoid projectiles and enemies as you fight your way through the levels.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257220/extras/d45dec4dafc5ef04f146b445c0ed27fb.poster.avif?t=1759284833\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257220/extras/d45dec4dafc5ef04f146b445c0ed27fb.webm?t=1759284833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257220/extras/d45dec4dafc5ef04f146b445c0ed27fb.mp4?t=1759284833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Battle large and challenging bosses to unlock your way to the next level.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257220/extras/ee3e47b0cd3c13fb91e17a56c0f3cb74.poster.avif?t=1759284833\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257220/extras/ee3e47b0cd3c13fb91e17a56c0f3cb74.webm?t=1759284833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257220/extras/ee3e47b0cd3c13fb91e17a56c0f3cb74.mp4?t=1759284833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Use Attribute blocks to upgrade and change your weapons and abilities in fun combinations.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257220/extras/eef68fb8b07e624d43429a1013a9ab93.poster.avif?t=1759284833\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257220/extras/eef68fb8b07e624d43429a1013a9ab93.webm?t=1759284833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257220/extras/eef68fb8b07e624d43429a1013a9ab93.mp4?t=1759284833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257220/extras/36e40ff37dd8235658a1df8eb8d2766b.avif?t=1759284833\" width=600 height=75 /></span><br><br>CyberVault is a fast paced bullet hell roguelike. You can upgrade your weapons and abilities as you collect attribute blocks. Highly customisable with lots of different combinations. Fight bosses, pick up items and improve your stats. Unlock new items and achievements for the next run through the ever-changing dungeon.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fight through procedurally generated levels full of enemies.<br></li><li>Battle unique bosses.<br></li><li>Upgrade your abilities with attribute blocks.</li></ul>",
